        "TileImage": "$($repository 2e1a30c5-b1e0-4984-b3f4-67f01f9ebfef).Image",
        "Description": "[URGENT TRANSMISSION REGARDING RECINDED CONTRACT]\rEFFECTIVE █████, 7/21/████ CONSIDER THE FOLLOWING CONTRACT AMENDED - NOTE ANY CHANGES AND EXECUTE ACCORDINGLY : \r\rKILL ORDER ID: 1241574\rCLIENT: ████████ █████████\rTARGET(S) (RESCINDED): SODERS, ERIC \rTARGET(S) (ACTIVE): NAKAMURA, AKIRA. YAMAZAKI, YUKI. SMITH, CARLTON.\rCONTRACT NET: $██,███,███\r\rNOTES: I know this is sudden, but Soders has given up TWO more providence operatives in exchange for immunity. This is a grand oppotunity.\r\rSieze it  -D",
